### Jemu.c amalgamated with SSE/SSE2, full SIB, ADC/SBB correctness, micro-ops, trace ring, soft breakpoints, and IMUL (0x69, 0x6B, 0F AF)

Below is a single-file, expanded implementation. It integrates:
- SSE/SSE2: MOVDQA/MOVDQU, MOVAPS/MOVAPD, MOVUPS/MOVUPD, AND/OR/XOR PS/PD, minimal SHUFPS
- Full SIB decode in 64-bit mode
- Correct ADC/SBB, refined INC/DEC flag effects
- Micro-ops layer for clarity and hotpaths
- Trace ring buffer and soft breakpoints
- IMUL two-operand variants: 0x69 (imm32), 0x6B (imm8), 0F AF (r/m)
- Kept your bare-metal-friendly style; SDL only for the framebuffer

You can drop this as jemu.c. Build and run as before.

```c
